You can also use native ComfyUI text encoding with these nodes instead of the original, the models are node specific and can't otherwise be mixed.

You can use either start image or reference image, or both.

For text to video you can use empty embeds or just disconnect images from the ImageToVideo Encode node.

Control and reference strength can be adjusted by adjusting the latent strength in the corresponding Encode node.
Adjust the blocks to swap based on your VRAM, this is a tradeoff between speed and memory usage.
Use any preprocessor you want here, depth is just an example
